    <div class="container">
        <div class="row section">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>We aim to minimize food wastage and maximize food security through a streamlined and efficient platform. By connecting food donors with recipient organizations, we help redistribute surplus food to those in need, reducing waste and alleviating hunger.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row section">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p>Our vision is a world where food is valued and not wasted, where everyone has access to sufficient, nutritious food. We strive to be at the forefront of the fight against food waste, fostering a community of responsible food consumption and distribution.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row section">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>Our Values</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Community:</strong> Building strong connections between donors and recipients to create a support network.</li>
                    <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Promoting sustainable practices to reduce food wastage and its environmental impact.</li>
                    <li><strong>Compassion:</strong> Caring for those in need by ensuring they have access to necessary resources.</li>
                    <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Utilizing technology to create efficient solutions for food redistribution.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row section">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>Our Impact</h2>
                <p>Since our inception, we have successfully redistributed thousands of meals to those in need. By partnering with local businesses, restaurants, and food producers, we have managed to make a significant impact on food security and waste reduction in our community. Our efforts have not only provided immediate relief to those facing hunger but have also raised awareness about the importance of sustainable food practices.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row section">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>Get Involved</h2>
                <p>There are many ways you can contribute to our mission:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Donate Food:</strong> If you are a business or individual with surplus food, you can donate it through our platform.</li>
                    <li><strong>Volunteer:</strong> Join our team of dedicated volunteers who help with food collection, distribution, and outreach.</li>
                    <li><strong>Partner with Us:</strong> If you are an organization that can benefit from food donations or want to support our cause, reach out to us for partnership opportunities.</li>
                    <li><strong>Spread the Word:</strong> Help us raise awareness by sharing our mission and efforts within your network.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
